txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: A collection of new sword sheaths from the goblins, Orcs, and other intelligent life surrounding Echad Candelleth. All items should be delivered to Bainthir at the camp.
'It is good to know that these have been destroyed. Thank you.'
'There are enemies here that are out of place, not of these lands, and they must be driven out and proof brought here.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: New Sword Sheaths
Bainthir, an Elf at the camp of Echad Candelleth, is awaiting a delivery of new sword sheaths.
Deliver the new sword sheaths to Bainthir at Echad Candelleth in the Trollshaws
You have accepted a task to collect new sword sheaths from the goblins, Orcs, and other intelligent life surrounding Echad Candelleth. You are to deliver the items to Bainthir at the camp.
Wanted: A collection of new sword sheaths from the goblins, Orcs, and other intelligent life surrounding Echad Candelleth.
